                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/346" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0056</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">8989 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">“东新恋”“国东恋”---东方航空股权争夺战</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">The Battle for the Equity of China Eastern Airlines</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">李春玲，王慧然</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国民航大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中国东方航空股份有限公司，新加坡航空公司，中国国际航空股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">交通运输业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">16 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">东航；新航；国航；并购；股权</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">China Eastern Airlines; Air China; Singapore Airlines; M&amp;amp;A; Equity</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2006年，中国东方航空股份有限公司（以下简称“东航”）遭遇 “滑铁卢”， 新加坡航空公司（以下简称“新航”）向东方航空抛出橄榄枝，“东新恋”由此开始，中国国际航空股份有限公司（以下简称“国航”）为打造超级承运人，想乘机入股东航，有意发展“国东恋”，并以“东航资产贱卖论”棒打鸳鸯，成功搅局“东新恋”。本案例着重从企业战略管理、财务管理及资本运作角度对案例中国航、新航、东航的动机和行为进行分析研究，并提出了在国有企业并购中政府职能转变及市场力量强化的问题，同时中国国有企业如何实现成功并购也应引人思考。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">In 2006, China Eastern Airlines was been in big trouble and encountered financial crisis, and Singapore Airlines want to get shares of China Eastern Airlines to expand its market share, so the love between China Eastern Airlines and Singapore Airlines had began. Air China, dreaming to build super-carrier of airlines, also intended to join in China Eastern Airlines. In order to defeat the Singapore Airlines, Air China declared that the assets of China Eastern Airlines had been underestimated and finally damaged the transaction between China Eastern Airlines and Singapore Airlines.
This case focuses on analyzing the motives and behaviors of China Airlines, Singapore Airlines and China Eastern Airlines in the case from the angle of strategic management、 financial management and capital operation, Besides, the case reminds the Government in merger of state-owned enterprises should transfer the functions and strengthen the market power and how to achieve successful mergers and acquisitions of state-owned enterprises in China should also be thought-provoking.
</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2008</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《工商管理》、《企业战略管理》、《财务管理》、《资本运作》、《公司治理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">资本运作、并购重组</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2011-02</td>
                            </tr>
